entry.title: DRACO Joins ECE at UCF
entry.content: The DRACO (Design of Resilient Architectures for Computing) Lab is pleased to join the Electrical and Computer Engineering Department at the University of Central Florida (UCF).
entry.summary: The DRACO (Design of Resilient Architectures for Computing) Lab is pleased to join the Electrical and Computer Engineering Department at the University of Central Florida (UCF).
